      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty\u2014it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it is still in absolute pristine condition inside and out. No scratches, no weird smells, just pure perfection. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. I'm looking for a smooth sale, so I've priced it to move quickly. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
