    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presented in museum-grade condition, this 996.2 Carrera features the definitive 3.6L M96/03 flat-six, delivering linear power through the VarioCam Plus system. The G96 6-speed manual transaxle is paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. Mechanical integrity is paramount: the IMS bearing has been retrofitted with a dual-row ceramic solution, and the rear main seal is bone dry. The chassis is sharpened by a corner-balanced Bilstein PSS10 coilover suite, while braking is handled by four-piston monoblock calipers over cross-drilled rotors. Clad in Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber on lightweight forged wheels, this example exhibits zero bore scoring and retains factory-spec compression ratios. The interior is an analog sanctuary with flawless upholstery and zero pixel degradation in the instrumentation.",
      "price": 44800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
