      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This is a collector-grade vehicle that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage since its original purchase. The exterior showcases flawless factory paint with a deep, mirror-like luster, free of any stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. The interior is equally pristine, featuring smoke-free leather that remains supple with no bolster wear, complemented by original floor mats and a cabin that retains its new-car scent. Every feature, from the advanced navigation system to the dual-zone climate control, operates perfectly. Mechanically, the car is exceptional; it comes with a comprehensive binder of every service record performed at the authorized dealership, including a recent major service and a fresh set of high-performance tires. This sale includes both original key fobs, the factory window sticker, and all owner's manuals. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a showroom-quality example that has been maintained with an open checkbook.",
